      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>1096</offset>
        <text>The very low abundance of genes for nitrification, the minor presence of anammox genes, the high potential for nitrogen fixation and mineralization and the potential for chemotrophic CO2 fixation and CO oxidation all provide potential clues on the anoxic zones functioning.
</text>
