      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1569</offset>
        <text>Overall, these results offer a more detailed perspective on the microbial ecology of anoxic environments and may help to develop new geochemical proxies to infer biology and chemistry interactions in ancient ecosystems.
</text>
